Package interfaces

Interface iEquipment

  • public interface iEquipment
    Interface defining interactions with equipment. This interface includes methods for checking the status of equipment, opening the equipment interface, and finding various equipment slots.

      • itemAt

        java.lang.Boolean itemAt​(EquipmentSlot equipmentSlot,
                         int itemToCheck,
                         java.awt.Color checkColor)
        Attempts to check for a specified itemID in the specified EquipmentSlot while also verifying a color on the item
        Parameters:
        equipmentSlot - uses the SDK enum EquipmentSlot
        itemToCheck - is the itemID you are looking for
        checkColor - the color to match the item with (for example the blue in a Rune scimitar)
        Returns:
        Boolean indicating whether the itemID was found in that equipment slot
